Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: San Francisco
Description: I've only been here twice. I thought people were exaggerating when they complained the water here in goleta was "so much worse" than san francisco tap water, but it turned out to be true.

Name: Yosemite National Park
Description: I saw a bison pooping from the family car here so that's cool. Or was it a buffalo??

Name: Stonebriar Mall
Description: THE mall where i used to live deep in the Texas suburbs. I can still exactly picture the ice skating rink in my mind, but apparently they got rid of it for more store space after I moved.

Name: The Nugget
Description: My high school jazz band stayed here when we went to the Reno Jazz Festival. Smells like cigarettes.

Name: The Getty
Description: Art museum. I don't particularly like it more than any other art museum, but I do like art museums more than the average place. The monorail up is cool.
